Package: box.shiny
Title: Engineering Shiny Apps using Modules and the {box} Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Jesse",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david.jesse@gmx.net")
Description: This package comes with functions that help you with engineering complex Shiny apps.
    Most importantly it lets you create template files for Shiny modules that use the {box}
    package, which allows for a clean and intuitive organization of your app project.
    Moreover, it supplies further useful functions, e.g. for creating helper functions or 
    R6 classes for your app.
